      </ingredient>
    </ingredients>
    <preparation>1. Cut baby spinach roughly
2. Cook spinach with oil and salt
3. Add chicken stock (or other soup) and cook for several minutes
4. Once reasonably soft shred spinach with blender and cook a little more.
5. Add cream and before serving the brown butter.

Cremespinat is often served with boiled and roasted potatoes 
plus fried egg, a classic in Austria.</preparation>
